  reg("c27.sum.b", "• Short stacks = low SPR, commit with top pair+.<br>• Push/fold with <15bb effective.<br>• ICM: tighten near bubble, avoid marginal spots.", "• 短筹码 = 低 SPR，顶对+可承诺。<br>• <15bb 有效筹码推/弃。<br>• ICM：泡沫附近打紧，避免边缘局面。");
  reg("concept.tournament", "Tournament/short stack", "锦标赛/短筹码");
  reg("c28.l1.t", "Plan from the flop", "从翻牌规划");
  reg("c28.l1.b", "Before betting, ask: which turns/rivers will I barrel? Which will I give up? Avoid betting with no plan.", "下注前先问：哪些转/河牌继续？哪些放弃？别无计划下注。");
  reg("c28.l2.t", "Three-street value", "三街价值");
  reg("c28.l2.b", "Strong hands (sets, two pair+) plan to bet three streets. Size so you can bet river.", "强牌（三条、两对+）规划三街下注。尺寸要能河牌再下注。");
  reg("c28.l3.t", "Give up lines", "放弃线");
  reg("c28.l3.b", "When the turn/river is bad for your range, check/give up. Don't barrel air on scare cards.", "转/河牌不利于你范围时过牌/放弃。别在吓人牌上开枪空气。");
  reg("c28.sum.t", "Key takeaways", "本课小结");
  reg("c28.sum.b", "• Plan flop → turn → river before betting.<br>• Strong hands: three-street value plan.<br>• Give up when board/runout favors villain.", "• 下注前规划翻→转→河。<br>• 强牌：三街价值计划。<br>• 牌面/发牌利于对手时放弃。");
  reg("concept.line_plan", "Multi-street planning", "多街规划");
  reg("c29.l1.t", "Paired boards", "配对面");
  reg("c29.l1.b", "Paired boards reduce straight/flush combos. Full houses and quads become possible. Bet less with one pair.", "配对面减少顺子/同花组合。葫芦与四条可能。单对少下注。");
  reg("c29.l2.t", "Monotone boards", "同色面");
  reg("c29.l2.b", "Three of one suit — flush draws everywhere. Need a spade/heart/etc. to bet. Check more without one.", "三张同花 — 处处同花听。需有该花色才下注。没有则多过牌。");
  reg("c29.l3.t", "Dynamic boards", "动态面");
  reg("c29.l3.b", "Connected, two-tone boards change nuts frequently. Size up with value and draws.", "连接、双花面坚果常变。价值与听牌加大尺寸。");
  reg("c29.sum.t", "Key takeaways", "本课小结");
  reg("c29.sum.b", "• Paired: full houses possible, one pair weaker.<br>• Monotone: need suit to bet; check without.<br>• Dynamic: size up, plan for changing nuts.", "• 配对：葫芦可能，单对更弱。<br>• 同色：需花色才下注；没有则过牌。<br>• 动态：加大尺寸，规划变化的坚果。");
  reg("concept.special_board", "Paired/monotone/special boards", "配对/同色/特殊牌面");
  reg("c30.l1.t", "Integrate concepts", "综合概念");
  reg("c30.l1.b", "Real spots combine sizing, blockers, SPR, and range dynamics. Identify the primary concept before acting.", "真实局面结合尺寸、阻断、SPR 与范围动态。行动前先识别主要概念。");
  reg("c30.l2.t", "Review key themes", "回顾要点");
  reg("c30.l2.b", "MDF vs small bets, fold medium vs big bets, value bet strong hands, bluff with blockers, plan multi-street.", "小注 MDF、大注弃中等、强牌价值下注、阻断牌诈唬、多街规划。");
  reg("c30.l3.t", "Trust the process", "相信流程");
  reg("c30.l3.b", "Work through: range advantage → board texture → your hand strength → villain's line → best action.", "按流程：范围优势 → 牌面纹理 → 牌力 → 对手线 → 最佳行动。");
  reg("c30.sum.t", "Key takeaways", "本课小结");
  reg("c30.sum.b", "• Identify the primary concept in each spot.<br>• MDF, blockers, SPR, pot control, and planning all apply.<br>• Work through range → board → hand → line → action.", "• 每题识别主要概念。<br>• MDF、阻断、SPR、控池、规划均适用。<br>• 按范围→牌面→牌力→线→行动。");
  reg("concept.capstone", "Capstone mixed spots", "综合实战");

